Additional modes within the app include Weapon roulette and Challenges. Weapon Roulette allows the excitement of Drop Roulette to extend to your weapon choice! 

The challenges add an extra layer for those players who want to add more risk to their game or just collect medals of achievement. Will you manage to earn the medallion for using a different weapon after each kill and then winning the game? Or the medallion for being the ultimate Warzone master and winning 10 matches?
